Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.97,0:21:00.05,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,何もいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:03.69,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたがいればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:06.80,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,そっと横顔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:10.35,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,息を殺す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.15,0:21:13.56,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,まばたきすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:17.22,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,消えてしまいそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:23.61,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,凝視めさせて　好きだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.46,0:21:27.43,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,あぁ　木々が震え
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:30.70,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,降り出した雪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:39.10,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,足跡ふたつ　白く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:46.15,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,時よ　積もれ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:53.12,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,髪に　胸に　ふたりだけの夢に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:22:06.99,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,咲けない 花の種は雪に抱かれ　寄り添うの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.53,0:22:15.09,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,静かに忘れられたい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.97,0:21:00.05,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:03.69,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有你在就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:06.80,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,偷偷看着你的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:10.35,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,屏住自己的呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.15,0:21:13.56,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛一眨眼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:17.22,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你就会消失不见似的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:23.61,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,让我永远注视下去吧 我最爱的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.46,0:21:27.43,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,摇曳的银树
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:30.70,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,飘落的白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:39.10,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,一双白色的足迹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:46.15,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,时光呀 堆积起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:53.12,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,堆积在头发上 在内心里 在仅属于两人的梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:22:06.99,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,没有开花的种子在白雪上依偎在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.53,0:22:15.09,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,想被静静地遗忘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.81,0:00:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于当时年幼的我们来说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.47,0:00:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界充满了威胁和威严
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只要长大成人获得咒力之后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.59,0:00:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中的恐惧应该会完全消失才对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直以来是这么坚信着的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.81,0:00:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现场的情况来判断
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本次战斗中的战损比..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是10:0
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是食虫虻部族的完全胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被打败的大黄蜂军士兵的遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.82,0:00:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一具的损伤都相当严重
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本都处于面目全非的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.42,0:00:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个以强大军事力为豪的大黄蜂部族
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:00:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然会如此轻易地被..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.89,0:00:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于奇狼丸本人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.81,0:00:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从战场遗留物进行综合判断之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.53,0:01:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认为它应该成功脱离了战斗区域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.52,0:01:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在仍然下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.77,0:01:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道和这次的事件是否有关..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.69,0:01:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大黄蜂军士兵的遗留物中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.58,0:01:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有发现任何一样武器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.08,0:01:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽有可能被胜方的食虫虻部族回收
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可既然如此的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.89,0:01:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法继续使用的武器通常会被遗弃在战场上才对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那个..总之
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们却完全找不到任何一件武器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.05,0:01:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听了刚才他的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有联想到什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.68,0:01:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天我去了一趟现场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那里已经采取了毁灭证据的措施
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.34,0:01:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有可燃物都处于一种完全炭化的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.62,0:01:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然特地采取这种措施..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说做了什么见不得人的事情吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.71,0:01:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这一点我有自己的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过并没有掌握确实的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想在讨论的最后才提出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食虫虻部族会不会是想隐瞒它的攻击手段呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早季 我不是说在那里等着你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年的怪物做的还蛮精致的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.98,0:02:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:37.00,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(448,360)}红花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要那个大的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥帮我捞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.27,0:03:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好一对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 正好一对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是怪物来了 会不会把它们吃掉呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.62,0:03:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.11,0:03:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它们放了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早季
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩子扮的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是你看错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可从来没听过让小孩子扮演怪物哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可能是今年才开始这么做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化鼠最近的急速进步和军备扩张
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说明它们有可能获得了某种情报源
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指拟蓑白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旧国家图书馆的移动式终端
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能还有数台幸存在外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化鼠们可能捕获了它们并从中获得了知识
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么瑞穗酱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你作为图书馆管理员对此有何见解？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻而易举地让大黄蜂全军覆没的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底存不存在呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁书 第四分类的..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据第四分类第三种..项目「殃」的内容来看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古代文明确实存在着几种大量破坏兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要使用它们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能瞬间将化鼠的军团消灭殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是炸弹之类的武器所造成的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.03,0:05:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真理亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真理亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真理亚..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:05:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早季..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看错了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是..她真的在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守也在..没有脸的少年也在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是前几天的实地检查时发现的大黄蜂军的箭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有没有发现到什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些箭上找不到任何损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其余的箭也全都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,残留在现场的所有大黄蜂军的箭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一支都以相同的状态保留了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果使用了炸弹之类的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物品是不可能像这样完整保留下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般来说用于攻击的箭..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论有没有射中目标
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,箭身上应该都会有所损伤才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般来说的话应该是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以常识来考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想保留下完好无损的箭..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:07:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有用咒力使其停留在半空中才能办到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肆星 不要再故弄玄虚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为到底发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算被扣上狂妄自大的骂名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要在这里说一说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让大黄蜂军全军覆没的..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是拥有咒力的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实..按照这个想法的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝比奈的报告也不存在前后矛盾了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是拥有咒力的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让大黄蜂军的所有武器失效了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那是相当高端的..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是这个镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是其他所有城镇之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不可能有人会做出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一点我敢保证
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么过去离开城镇的人类又如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些遗骨又如何说明呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今 连这一点都让人不禁生疑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为宣称发现遗骨并送回镇中的..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:08:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那位被认为是本次事件元凶的野狐丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:07.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然工序稍许费时费力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是顺利的话我等也许还能提供遗骨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把遗骨送回镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下认为他们应该就能接受了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我等的遗骨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在某些部位上和神明大人的极为相似
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如是特别身长的个体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小和年轻神明大人也并无二致
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以把它的遗骨 用石头细心打磨一番..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些遗骨是绝对是货真价实的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.36,0:08:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遗骨经过了极为慎重的层层鉴定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是人类遗骨无误
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年龄和性别也并无矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后还进行了DNA鉴定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而最终让我们做出断定的..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是保存在和贵园的两人的牙印
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:08:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋月真理亚和伊东守两人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经确认已经100%死亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以和那两人是无关的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早季..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕是幽灵..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能见到真理亚他们的话我也想见上一面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道你一定看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是早在来祭典之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早季就预感到能在这里见到真理亚他们了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的浴衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和去年完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像丧服一样..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天大家都会从冥土归来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这并没有什么好奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早季见到真理亚他们了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于隶属于食虫虻部族
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及同盟之部族的所有化鼠..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与会全员一致赞成并批准将它们全数驱除·抹杀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以干为首的这五位鸟兽保护官将立刻执行此决议
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我最后有一个提案
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于一周之后举行的夏之祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在确认安全之前是否应该进行延期呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否决！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然因惧怕区区化鼠..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.37,0:10:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而将期待已久的祭典延期
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本是闻所未闻！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这胆小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有其他疑问了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么散会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.43,0:10:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天遇上了那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为祭典会延期
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是能如期举行还是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看啊 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说吧 确实有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么八丁标内会出现蚊子？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是干先生他们回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了吗..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 食虫虻驱除行动的期限好像到今天为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人..有人倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.92,0:11:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成..是刚才的孩子..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是孩子..是化鼠！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会..这不可能啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们深知自己将惨遭灭族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:11:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以打算来拼个你死我活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:11:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说食虫虻来袭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.29,0:12:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须赶紧通知大伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？烟火爆炸了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个 我们必须赶紧逃离这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊..它们打算对广场进行夹击！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对面很有可能也有敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去广场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是广场不是..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在广场上的人们不会坐以待毙的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形式可能已经逆转了才对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:13:00.65,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了避免发生干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家请封印自己的咒力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里由我来接战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欺骗人类的恶鼠..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扯了它们的舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翻出它们的内脏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挂在太阳底下晒成肉干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然就碾碎它们的骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉长它们的躯干
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叠成三层做成肉饼来吃吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的那帮家伙..为什么从上风处..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是这样吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是毒气 大家请小心！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.16,0:14:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子倒也并不是傻瓜啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上风处？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的那帮家伙为什么没有从
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能用气味确定我们位置的下风处出现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是从上风处攻过来了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然改变了风向..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪门歪道！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉碎吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区拟态..真以为能瞒得过本人的眼睛么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这群鼠辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本大爷居然..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被区区鼠辈..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 如果不是我粗心大意的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何天神之子..肉体是如此脆弱..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:17:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我体内的..艺术家..命绝于此..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是何等地浪费..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让美之..残像..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危机已暂时退却
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现状依然不能掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全保障会议的成员们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在此列中的话 请立即集合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后的行动按照异常事态训练
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以五人一组进行行动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:17:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果小组有缺员状况的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请立刻跟其他小组汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.78,0:18:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共同行动的人数绝不能少于五人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦组成小组之后就在镇中进行巡逻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把残留下来的化鼠全数清除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:15.28,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,不管它们宣称自己对人类效忠或是跪地求饶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:17.08,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要予以理会 一旦发现立即抹杀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早季！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 他也平安哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.38,0:18:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医疗方面的有关人员请在此集合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行走不方便的伤员请送至公民礼堂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富子女士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸟饲小姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是个最爱操心 最为谨慎的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只有宏美酱提议应该延期夏之祭典啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完人学校的一班只剩我们俩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和其他人汇合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不知怎么的 我现在担心的不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.39,0:19:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要各处小心哦 早季
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别仗着自己拥有咒力就单独行动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在和那个恶鬼..K遭遇以来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还从未体会过如此强烈的憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只令人恨之入骨的化鼠..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:20:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野狐丸必须受到应有的报应
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.64,0:20:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在此发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会让它在任何生物都从未体验过的痛苦之中..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点一滴地失去生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.39,0:20:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋月真理亚 十四岁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十二年前和伊东守一起逃离神栖66町之后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人都已确认死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢早季
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是..也不能让守孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何我也无法在那个镇子中活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且两个女生之间生不了孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样呢 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.47,0:22:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别..别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.56,0:22:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那..到底是什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃吧..快点..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.63,0:22:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙要回来了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.02,0:22:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙指的是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.76,0:22:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么？
